<span id="freeTextContainer3860378585514350687">A spectacular book on Science written in the 1960s but much ahead of its time, delving into the basics of numbers to fundamental physics , genetics and cosmology( in which the author is a pioneer). Very lucidly explained and quite captivating &amp; it is a treat for an inquisitive reader.</span>

